"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"真係冇得輸!多謝手足!"},{"pid":"08180df995e198f13b9b42e646ba75eca7f2b94e","tid":1773574,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f56494b2cea779a5353a6391b00f87a42f2031e","tid":1773574,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"唔係好熟佢地仲支唔支持共產主義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"反共"},{"pid":"aa574efc072ac89c1d3abe0ea73020d1cf5320ba","tid":1773574,"uid":279844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8f56494b2cea779a5353a6391b00f87a42f2031e","tid":1773574,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"唔係好熟佢地仲支唔支持共產主義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"每個地方都實有共黨餘孽，但佢地普遍憎共產黨到痴線，程度同憎納粹不相伯仲，因為俄羅斯其實歷史上都唔係第一次侵略佢地，同埋佢地被共產黨整死左好多人。<br />\n<br />\n而家歐洲好多國家都立左法禁止公眾宣揚納粹，但波蘭早幾年再立左條法，係禁止宣揚共產主義<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8E%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%258C%2596&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=fbe11849\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8E%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%8C%96</a>"},{"pid":"b1d875a662f7cea3d6af79e734ad1c6971997776","tid":1773574,"uid":194143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手足好撚嘢<br />\n唔係唔推嘛"},{"pid":"271797a5554f7a891482848a690106767b9d3bd5","tid":1773574,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"314895c00438d6816440de0667d16c6b3567124d","tid":1773574,"uid":279844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa574efc072ac89c1d3abe0ea73020d1cf5320ba","tid":1773574,"uid":279844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8f56494b2cea779a5353a6391b00f87a42f2031e","tid":1773574,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"唔係好熟佢地仲支唔支持共產主義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"每個地方都實有共黨餘孽，但佢地普遍憎共產黨到痴線，程度同憎納粹不相伯仲，因為俄羅斯其實歷史上都唔係第一次侵略佢地，同埋佢地被共產黨整死左好多人。<br />\n<br />\n而家歐洲好多國家都立左法禁止公眾宣揚納粹，但波蘭早幾年再立左條法，係禁止宣揚共產主義<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8E%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%258C%2596&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=fbe11849\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8E%BB%E5%85%B1%E5%8C%96</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"「波蘭2016年5月實施《去共產主義法》，禁止宣傳共產主義、專制極權制度，全國各地更改廣場、街道、道路、橋樑等具有共產主義、專制極權制度色彩的命名與地名。2017年10月21日再施行修正案，一年內要推倒境內所有象徵共產主義、專制極權的塑像、紀念碑、路堤、浮雕及各種標誌。」"},{"pid":"bc006eda85516beb009321b014185482542cf556","tid":1773574,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:16:16.000Z","msg":"Thank you"},{"pid":"c64130daad7ad31e33e4a6019b4c7e769122d081","tid":1773574,"uid":210895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96e148f5384a8b488ed10f02f5a51cd6b6f1d8e9","tid":1773574,"uid":32180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e50c71b11bcb4183dc5511f9a9b0235795708e04","tid":1773574,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321a8311a0467413fd140ddcd3ba738fe1e6d881","tid":1773574,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"